      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. While it currently starts, the engine exhibits a noticeable knock and the transmission slips significantly between gears. The exterior shows substantial rust and several large dents, while the interior requires a deep cleaning and repair of the torn upholstery. This car would be best suited as a project for a mechanic or as a source for parts.",
